<indexterm zone="ch-system-openssh"><primary sortas="a-openssh">OpenSSH</primary></indexterm>

<sect2 role="package"><title/>
<para> The OpenSSH package contains ssh clients and the sshd daemon. This is useful
for encrypting authentication and subsequent traffic over a network..</para>

<segmentedlist>
<segtitle>&buildtime;</segtitle>
